## ğŸ”Š Step 4 â€” Live Noise Cancellation Error (Common Fix)

If you see errors like:

* noise_cancellation not found
* module not installed
* audio stream failed

Do this:

### 1. Reinstall plugin


pip uninstall livekit-plugins-noise-cancellation -y
pip install livekit-plugins-noise-cancellation


---

### 2. Install audio backend


pip install sounddevice pyaudio


Windows users (if pyaudio fails):


pip install pipwin
pipwin install pyaudio


---

### 3. Restart terminal

Close terminal completely.

Reopen:

Activate env:


.venv\Scripts\activate


Run again:


python brain.py console


---

## ğŸ” Step 5 â€” Import All Tools into brain.py

If JARVIS tools are not working with voice:

Make sure brain.py imports:

* file tools
* window control
* keyboard/mouse
* memory system

Then agent.py should only start brain.

Architecture:

agent.py â†’ brain.py â†’ tools

This avoids confusion.

